# Coding Rules

## General Coding Guidelines
- Use consistent naming conventions for variables and functions
- Use consistent indentation and formatting
- Use consistent commenting conventions
- Use consistent error handling conventions
- Use consistent logging conventions
- Use consistent debugging conventions
- Use consistent testing conventions
- Use consistent documentation conventions
- Use consistent code organization conventions
- Don't include thinking comments in the code (internal conversations with yourself)